---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/Container.astro";
import MenuButton from "@components/MenuButton.astro";
---

<Layout title="RetroBooks">
  <main>
    <Container>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 lg:grid-cols-2 text-white">
        <div class="p-10 text-white">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-white">
            <div class="col-span-3">
              <h2 class="md:text-5xl text-2xl">RetroBooks By RetroKode</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 my-4">
                <img
                  class="w-10 lg:w-10 xl:w-10"
                  src="./svgs/mac_mini.svg"
                  alt="MAC"
                />
                <img
                  class="w-10 lg:w-10 xl:w-10"
                  src="./svgs/apple_logo.svg"
                  alt="Apple Logo"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 my-4">
                <img
                  class="w-10 lg:w-10 xl:w-10"
                  src="./svgs/windows.svg"
                  alt="Workstation"
                />
                <img
                  class="w-10 lg:w-10 xl:w-10"
                  src="./svgs/google_play.svg"
                  alt="Google Play Logo"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="my-10">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent et
            enim aliquam, gravida velit in, tristique augue. Etiam maximus nulla
            sed quam egestas, ac dignissim dui ornare. Mauris suscipit et lorem
            eget volutpat. Aliquam tincidunt nisl ante, at tincidunt nulla
            elementum in. Aliquam at nunc pretium, tristique justo id, semper
            risus. Cras viverra efficitur enim ut ornare.
          </p>
          <p class="my-10">
            Curabitur a odio ornare, hendrerit arcu non, convallis nulla.
            Praesent convallis, nibh et dapibus interdum, est nunc ornare ipsum,
            eget convallis metus ante id ipsum. Praesent at purus id tellus
            aliquam gravida ac ac dolor. Sed malesuada turpis nec mauris commodo
            auctor. Etiam fringilla mauris id est bibendum faucibus. Quisque
            eget lectus mi. Cras eget dolor mollis, sodales ante vitae,
            elementum neque.
          </p>
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 grid-cols-1 gap-2">
            <div class="col-span-1 m-auto">
              <a
                class="group transition text-white"
                href="/download"
                title="Download"
              >
                <MenuButton
                  text="DOWNLOAD"
                  rounded="true"
                  border="true"
                  color="retro-green"
                />
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1">
              <a href="/premium" title="UPGRADE YOUR VERSION">
                <MenuButton
                  text="UPGRADE YOUR VERSION"
                  rounded="true"
                  border="true"
                  color="retro-yellow"
                />
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-10">
          <span class="my-5">The commitment to revive the love of reading.</span
          >
          <img
            class="w-45 lg:w-45 xl:w-45 mx-2"
            src="./svgs/book.svg"
            alt={`Book`}
          />
          <span
            >Reading can always be pleasurable if you choose to do it in the
            best way!</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </main>
</Layout>
